body.raw:
I did a write-up and a live stream about how NextAuth.js works at the source level, released as a Tour De Source article in collaboration with Sourcegraph.
Huge thanks to the Sourcegraph folks and [@Balázs Orbán](https://twitter.com/balazsorban44) for reviewing the document. You can check it out at:

- [Sourcegraph notebook](https://sourcegraph.com/notebooks/Tm90ZWJvb2s6MTc2MQ==)
- [Twitch live stream highlight](https://www.twitch.tv/videos/1627753164)
- [Reddit post](https://www.reddit.com/r/nextjs/comments/y86b8o/how_nextauthjs_and_auth_protocols_work/?utm_source=share&utm_medium=web2x&context=3)

I hope that in the spirit of Hacktoberfest, this document helps you to contribute to NextAuth.js.
